  <brief_title>Mortality Analysis of ST Elevation Myocardial Infarction (STEMI) Patients in Belgium</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Observational Study to Assess Predictors of in Hospital Mortality in STEMI Patients Admitted in Belgian Hospitals</official_title>
